<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.2">
<l>ticaikkiṉṟa tēyiva ṇōyitu mikka perunteyva</l>
<l>micaippiṉṟi nīraṇaṅ kāṭu miḷanteyva maṉṟitu</l>
<l>ticaippiṉṟi yēcaṅku cakkara meṉṟivaḷ kēṭkanī</l>
<l>ricaikkiṟṟi rāki ṉaṉṟē yilpeṟumitu kāṇmiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She subsides to pain. This [is] the very great god,</l>
<l>this [is] not the young god to whom you dance as demonesses, without playing music.</l>
<l>If you intone, for her to hear, “the conch, the discus”,</l>
<l>without amazement, [it] will be good. This will hit home, see.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
